    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pork is browning, peel and chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>green</strong> <strong>chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>orange[s]</strong> in half, then peel and roughly chop <strong>half</strong> the <strong>orange[s] </strong>and set aside</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1690477253539-x200.jpg",
