      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>udon noodles</strong> and<strong> spinach</strong> to the pan with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and cook, covered, for 2-3 min or until the spinach has started to wilt</p><p>Tip: Gently separate the noodles with a fork!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1690477268413-x200.jpg",
