            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once wilted, add the <strong>orange nam jim sauce</strong> and <strong>chopped orange</strong> to the pan and mix it all together</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until the sauce has slightly thickened, the noodles are fully coated and the mince is cooked through (no pink meat!) – these are your<strong> sticky nam jim pork & orange udon noodles</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
